==================================================
CORENAV PLUGIN API SPECIFICATION
Version 1.0 Draft

PURPOSE

The Plugin API allows third-party developers to
extend CoreNav without modifying the core source.

Plugins shall be capable of extending:

* User Interfaces
* File Operations
* Terminal Systems
* Editors
* Build Systems
* Languages
* Security Systems
* Device Management
* Network Services
* Cloud Services

