PLUGIN MANIFEST

plugin.toml

Required Fields

* Name
* Version
* Author
* License
* Description
* Permissions
* Dependencies

Optional Fields

* Homepage
* Repository
* Documentation
* Supported Interfaces
* Minimum CoreNav Version

