PERMISSION SYSTEM

Plugins must explicitly request permissions.

Available Permissions

Filesystem.Read
Filesystem.Write
Filesystem.Delete
Filesystem.Execute

Network.Client
Network.Server

Terminal.Access

Editor.Access

Workspace.Access

Plugin.Access

Privilege.Request

System.Monitor

Device.Access

Cloud.Access

==================================================
PLUGIN SANDBOXING

Default State

Sandboxed

Optional Modes

* Sandboxed
* Restricted
* Trusted

No plugin may obtain elevated privileges without
explicit authorization.

